{
  "stem": "13817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some guy in SS uniform standing there-- out, out-- with a whip in his hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as you came out, you was-- was whipped already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And line up in rows of five.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody line up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was-- put your luggage in one pile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It will be brought after you into the-- into where you're going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some guys in striped uniforms running around, some with whips in their hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some were just putting the-- the luggage all in one-- the one spot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we still didn't know where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there on the other side, there was a other rail tracks, where one train was unloaded for-- you could see people coming right out of Europe, still dressed in European-- still dressed in-- in Sunday dresses and good dresses.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people started to being separated-- women and men, and children with the old people and the women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's a just a-- a man-made confusion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, we were march right into the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But the other ones were marched by somebody who said, to the right, to the left because we were-- we came all from a work camp already.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one-- one-- some of them guys in the uniforms-- well, you in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have any idea where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were-- there were incidents, which I never have talk about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't think I want to-- what happened to people there when they were coming off the trains and--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The thing is too-- too crass, too cruel to even talk about it because today, I ask myself if it-- if it a dream or-- or it really happened because this was things-- not-- humans wouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
